    "subtype": "vehicle",
    "text": "This huge, magical clockwork rover moves on a continuous band of heavy treads, which make it easier to for the device to navigate across various adverse conditions. It contains magical clockwork birds which can transmit visual information back to the surveyor.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
